222
00:40:56,719 --> 00:40:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači živiš sada, gledaš u vječnost.

223
00:40:59,679 --> 00:41:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je ta čistoća, odnosno abstinencija moguća.

224
00:41:03,599 --> 00:41:07,840
